{
  "openapi": "3.0.3",
  "info": {
    "title": "SSLCommerz Subscription Payment API",
    "description": "SSLCommerz payment backend — AHTM Property Management.\n\n## 🚀 Payment Flow (Flutter WebView)\n1. **POST /api/payment/init** call করো → `gatewayPageURL` পাবে\n2. User কে ওই URL এ redirect করো (WebView / browser)\n3. User bKash/Nagad/Card দিয়ে pay করে\n4. Success হলে **Subscription auto-activate** হয়ে যাবে\n5. User কে `success_url` এ redirect করবে (dynamic URL support)\n\n## 🔄 Dynamic Redirect URLs (Flutter WebView)\nPayment init করার সময় `success_url`, `fail_url`, `cancel_url` pass করলে payment শেষে সেই URL এ redirect হবে।\nনা দিলে server এর `/payment-result` page এ fallback করবে।\n\n## 💰 Pricing\n| Plan Type | Price/Unit/Month | 3 Months | 6 Months | Yearly (20% off) |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| Self Managed | ৳200 | ৳600/unit | ৳1,200/unit | ৳1,920/unit |\n| Company Managed | ৳1,500 | ৳4,500/unit | ৳9,000/unit | ৳14,400/unit |\n\n## 📋 API Overview\n| # | Method | Endpoint | Description |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| 1 | POST | /api/payment/init | ⭐ Payment শুরু করো |\n| 2 | GET | /api/payment/status/{transactionId} | Payment status চেক করো |\n| 3 | GET | /api/subscription/plans | Plans ও Pricing দেখো |\n| 4 | GET | /api/subscription/user/{userId} | Active Subscription দেখো |\n| 5 | GET | /api/subscription/user/{userId}/history | Subscription History |\n| 6 | POST | /api/subscription/calculate-price | Price Preview |\n| 7 | POST | /api/subscription/check-validity | Subscription Valid কিনা চেক করো |\n| 8 | POST | /api/payment/success | 🔒 SSLCommerz callback (auto) |\n| 9 | POST | /api/payment/fail | 🔒 SSLCommerz callback (auto) |\n| 10 | POST | /api/payment/cancel | 🔒 SSLCommerz callback (auto) |\n| 11 | POST | /api/payment/ipn | 🔒 SSLCommerz IPN (auto) |\n| 12 | GET | /payment-result | Payment result HTML page |",
    "version": "2.1.0",
    "contact": {
      "name": "AHTM Support"
    }
  },
  "servers": [
    { "url": "http://localhost:5000", "description": "Local Development" },
    { "url": "https://your-production-url.com", "description": "Production (change this)" }
  ],
  "tags": [
    { "name": "⭐ Payment", "description": "Payment init + status check — Flutter থেকে এই APIs call করবে" },
    { "name": "📋 Subscription", "description": "Plans, user subscription, validity check, price calculator" },
    { "name": "🔒 SSLCommerz Callbacks", "description": "SSLCommerz internally calls these — Flutter থেকে call করার দরকার নেই" },
    { "name": "📄 Pages", "description": "Server-rendered HTML pages" }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/api/payment/init": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["⭐ Payment"],
        "summary": "⭐ Payment শুরু করো (ONLY this 1 API needed for payment)",
        "description": "Full payment + subscription activation এই 1 API তেই হয়ে যাবে।\n\n**Flow:**\n1. এই API call করো user info + plan info দিয়ে\n2. Response এ `gatewayPageURL` পাবে\n3. User কে ওই URL এ redirect করো (Flutter WebView)\n4. User bKash/Nagad/Card দিয়ে pay করে\n5. Success হলে subscription auto-activate হবে\n6. User কে `success_url` এ redirect করবে (query params সহ)\n\n**Dynamic Redirect URLs:**\n- `success_url` দিলে: `success_url?status=success&tran_id=xxx&subscription_id=yyy`\n- `fail_url` দিলে: `fail_url?status=fail&tran_id=xxx`\n- `cancel_url` দিলে: `cancel_url?status=cancelled&tran_id=xxx`\n- কোনো URL না দিলে: `/payment-result?status=...` page এ fallback\n\n**Server বাকি সব automatically handle করে (callbacks, validation, activation).**",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": { "$ref": "#/components/schemas/PaymentInitRequest" },
              "examples": {
                "with_redirect_urls": {
                  "summary": "With dynamic redirect URLs (recommended for Flutter WebView)",
                  "value": {
                    "userId": "firebase_user_uid_123",
                    "customerName": "Sazzad",
                    "customerEmail": "sazzad@example.com",
                    "customerPhone": "01700000000",
                    "customerAddress": "Dhaka, Bangladesh",
                    "planType": "self_managed",
                    "planKey": "3m",
                    "units": 2,
                    "success_url": "https://yourapp.com/payment/success",
                    "fail_url": "https://yourapp.com/payment/fail",
                    "cancel_url": "https://yourapp.com/payment/cancel"
                  }
                },
                "without_redirect_urls": {
                  "summary": "Without redirect URLs (uses server fallback page)",
                  "value": {
                    "userId": "firebase_user_uid_123",
                    "customerName": "Sazzad",
                    "customerEmail": "sazzad@example.com",
                    "customerPhone": "01700000000",
                    "planType": "company_managed",
                    "planKey": "1y",
                    "units": 5
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "✅ Payment session created — redirect user to `gatewayPageURL`",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "example": {
                  "success": true,
                  "message": "Payment session created",
                  "data": {
                    "subscriptionId": "65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1",
                    "orderId": "ORD_1740307200000",
                    "transactionId": "SSL_firebase_user_uid_123_1740307200000",
                    "gatewayPageURL": "https://sandbox.sslcommerz.com/EasyCheckOut/testcde123",
                    "sessionKey": "A1B2C3D4E5F6G7H8",
                    "amount": 1200,
                    "currency": "BDT",
                    "planType": "self_managed",
                    "planLabel": "3 Months",
                    "planKey": "3m",
                    "units": 2,
                    "pricePerUnit": 200,
                    "startDate": "2026-03-09T00:00:00.000Z",
                    "endDate": "2026-06-09T00:00:00.000Z"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "❌ Validation error",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "examples": {
                  "missing_fields": {
                    "summary": "Required fields missing",
                    "value": {
                      "success": false,
                      "message": "Missing required fields",
                      "requiredFields": {
                        "userId": "string (Firebase UID)",
                        "customerName": "string",
                        "customerEmail": "string",
                        "customerPhone": "string",
                        "planType": "self_managed | company_managed",
                        "planKey": "3m | 6m | 1y",
                        "units": "number (min 1)"
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  "invalid_planType": {
                    "summary": "Invalid planType",
                    "value": {
                      "success": false,
                      "message": "Invalid planType. Must be 'self_managed' or 'company_managed'"
                    }
                  },
                  "invalid_planKey": {
                    "summary": "Invalid planKey",
                    "value": {
                      "success": false,
                      "message": "Invalid planKey. Must be '3m', '6m', or '1y'"
                    }
                  },
                  "ssl_session_failed": {
                    "summary": "SSLCommerz session creation failed",
                    "value": {
                      "success": false,
                      "message": "Failed to create payment session",
                      "details": null
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "500": {
            "description": "Server error",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "example": { "success": false, "message": "Internal server error", "error": "Error details" }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/payment/status/{transactionId}": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["⭐ Payment"],
        "summary": "Payment Status চেক করো",
        "description": "Transaction ID দিয়ে payment ও subscription status চেক করো।\nPayment complete হয়েছে কিনা, subscription active কিনা — সব দেখতে পাবে।",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "transactionId",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "description": "Transaction ID (payment init এর response এ পাওয়া যায়)",
            "schema": { "type": "string" },
            "example": "SSL_firebase_user_uid_123_1740307200000"
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "✅ Payment status found",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "example": {
                  "success": true,
                  "data": {
                    "subscriptionId": "65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1",
                    "orderId": "ORD_1740307200000",
                    "transactionId": "SSL_firebase_user_uid_123_1740307200000",
                    "planType": "self_managed",
                    "planLabel": "3 Months",
                    "planKey": "3m",
                    "units": 2,
                    "pricePerUnit": 200,
                    "totalPrice": 1200,
                    "startDate": "2026-03-09T00:00:00.000Z",
                    "endDate": "2026-06-09T00:00:00.000Z",
                    "paymentStatus": "completed",
                    "paymentMethod": "sslcommerz",
                    "isActive": true,
                    "isExpired": false,
                    "isValid": true,
                    "daysRemaining": 89,
                    "createdAt": "2026-03-09T00:00:00.000Z"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "404": {
            "description": "❌ Payment not found",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "example": { "success": false, "message": "Payment not found" }
              }
            }
          },
          "500": {
            "description": "Server error",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "example": { "success": false, "message": "Internal server error" }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/subscription/plans": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["📋 Subscription"],
        "summary": "Plans ও Pricing দেখো",
        "description": "Available subscription plans ও pricing return করে।\n\n**Self Managed:** ৳200/unit/month\n**Company Managed:** ৳1,500/unit/month\n**Yearly:** 20% discount",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "✅ Available plans with pricing",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "example": {
                  "success": true,
                  "data": {
                    "self_managed": {
                      "name": "Self Managed",
                      "description": "User manages units & tenants themselves",
                      "pricePerUnit": 200,
                      "currency": "BDT",
                      "durations": {
                        "3m": { "label": "3 Months", "months": 3, "discount": 0, "totalPerUnit": 600 },
                        "6m": { "label": "6 Months", "months": 6, "discount": 0, "totalPerUnit": 1200 },
                        "1y": { "label": "Yearly", "months": 12, "discount": 20, "totalPerUnit": 1920 }
                      }
                    },
                    "company_managed": {
                      "name": "Company Managed",
                      "description": "Company handles full management",
                      "pricePerUnit": 1500,
                      "currency": "BDT",
                      "durations": {
                        "3m": { "label": "3 Months", "months": 3, "discount": 0, "totalPerUnit": 4500 },
                        "6m": { "label": "6 Months", "months": 6, "discount": 0, "totalPerUnit": 9000 },
                        "1y": { "label": "Yearly", "months": 12, "discount": 20, "totalPerUnit": 14400 }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/subscription/user/{userId}": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["📋 Subscription"],
        "summary": "Active Subscription দেখো",
        "description": "User এর active subscription আছে কিনা চেক করো।\n\n**Logic:**\n1. `isActive == true` query করে\n2. `paymentStatus == 'completed'` && `!isExpired` filter করে\n3. `endDate` দিয়ে sort করে latest টা return করে\n4. Expired subscription থাকলে auto-deactivate করে",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "userId",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "description": "Firebase UID",
            "schema": { "type": "string" },
            "example": "firebase_user_uid_123"
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Subscription info",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "examples": {
                  "active": {
                    "summary": "✅ Active subscription found",
                    "value": {
                      "success": true,
                      "hasActiveSubscription": true,
                      "data": {
                        "subscriptionId": "65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1",
                        "orderId": "ORD_1740307200000",
                        "transactionId": "SSL_firebase_user_uid_123_1740307200000",
                        "planType": "self_managed",
                        "planLabel": "3 Months",
                        "planKey": "3m",
                        "units": 2,
                        "pricePerUnit": 200,
                        "totalPrice": 1200,
                        "startDate": "2026-03-09T00:00:00.000Z",
                        "endDate": "2026-06-09T00:00:00.000Z",
                        "paymentStatus": "completed",
                        "paymentMethod": "sslcommerz",
                        "isActive": true,
                        "isExpired": false,
                        "isValid": true,
                        "daysRemaining": 89,
                        "createdAt": "2026-03-09T00:00:00.000Z"
                      }
                    }
                  },
                  "none": {
                    "summary": "❌ No active subscription",
                    "value": {
                      "success": true,
                      "hasActiveSubscription": false,
                      "message": "No active subscription found",
                      "data": null
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "500": {
            "description": "Server error",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "example": { "success": false, "message": "Internal server error" }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/api/subscription/user/{userId}/history": {
